						               													<description>Ledici Dice Football is a very small game consisting of only 3 custom dice, which attempts to simulate a football game. The game is published by Ledici.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Components: &amp;#10;Drawstring Bag&amp;#10;Rules Leaflet&amp;#10;3 Custom D6's (Blue, Green and Red)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The aim of the game is to 'score' more goals than your oppenent within a certain time. Rules state &amp;quot;Players decide the druation of their game before they start or they play for as long as the wish.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game itself is pure luck, the starting player rolls the blue dice and follows an action based on the roll. There is a 1 in 6 chance that this will mean the green dice can be rolled. Rolling the green dice is the only way to score a goal, again a 1 in 6 chance. Additionally the red dice can be brought into play which contains penalties, inluding a concede a goal side.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The theme feels thin at best in what is essentially just a blind rolling game with no strategy at all possible. The rules state the game can be played solo, however no rules are provided to this end.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
